	<section id="primary" class="content-area category-environment tag-air-pollution tag-asthma tag-berkshire-hathaway tag-calenergy tag-clean-energy-goals tag-dust-clouds tag-electric-cars tag-electric-vehicles tag-environmental-justice tag-environmental-protection tag-geothermal tag-imperial-county tag-imperial-valley tag-lead-contamination tag-lithium tag-lithium-valley-commission tag-respiratory-problems tag-salton-sea">
